data.title: 准备以至少30秒的时间回答以下问题
data.answer: The photo shoots a young Caucasian man wearing a navy top with red letters on it and a pair of blue jeans is kicked by his friend on his face. His friend who is kicking him wears the jeans with the same blue color and a pair of white sneakers while holding a mug. His other friend is watching them at the back.
